  "title": "Enum TextureParameter",
  "content": "<h1 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameter' data-commentId='T:Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameter' id='Alis_Core_Graphic_OpenGL_Enums_TextureParameter'>Enum TextureParameter    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Graphic/src/OpenGL/Enums/TextureParameter.cs#L35'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h1>\r\n <div class=\"facts text-secondary\">\r\n<dl><dt>Namespace</dt><dd><a href='Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.html'>Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums</a></dd></dl><dl><dt>Assembly</dt><dd>Alis.dll</dd></dl>\r\n</div><p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The texture parameter enum</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public enum TextureParameter</code></pre><h2 class='section'>Fields</h2><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>Nearest = 9728</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The nearest texture parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>Linear = 9729</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The linear texture parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>NearestMipMapNearest = 9984</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The nearest mip map nearest texture parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>LinearMipMapNearest = 9985</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The linear mip map nearest texture parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>NearestMipMapLinear = 9986</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The nearest mip map linear texture parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>LinearMipMapLinear = 9987</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The linear mip map linear texture parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>ClampToEdge = 33071</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The clamp to edge texture parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>ClampToBorder = 33069</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The clamp to border texture parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>MirrorClampToEdge = 34627</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The mirror clamp to edge texture parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>MirroredRepeat = 33648</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The mirrored repeat texture parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>Repeat = 10497</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The repeat texture parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>Red = 6403</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The red texture parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>Green = 6404</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The green texture parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>Blue = 6405</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The blue texture parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>Alpha = 6406</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The alpha texture parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>Zero = 0</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The zero texture parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>One = 1</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The one texture parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>CompareRefToTexture = 34894</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The compare ref to texture texture parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>None = 0</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The none texture parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>StencilIndex = 6401</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The stencil index texture parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>DepthComponent = 6402</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The depth component texture parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>MaxAnisotropyExt = 34046</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The max anisotropy ext texture parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl>",
